headline: Equifax (NYSE:EFX) Beats Q3 Sales Expectations
summary: Credit reporting giant Equifax (NYSE:EFX) reported Q3 CY2025 results exceeding the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 7.2% year on year to $1.54 billion. The company expects next quarter’s revenue to be around $1.52 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.04 per share was 5.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Equifax: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
